://lih.kg/2162097</a>"},{"pid":"196fc5a070b5b055f2e3710d590a3757f8597007","tid":2161246,"uid":155371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"死臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae32608ac3ae96c9b8966a9da182100c9990b59d","tid":2161246,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"葛博士幾時會用普通話開記者會？"},{"pid":"875b9f28785d5df12979703823b7ca558157cf11","tid":2161246,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"係唔俾吹咩"},{"pid":"246318be149c5b5368a95f604c2511e2dd9232bf","tid":2161246,"uid":7609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"建議你班死賤種由今日起用普通話講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ed7263f4dd405b228d8d528a62c91b28fbb570","tid":2161246,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"葛佩煩自己唔識做就搞人"},{"pid":"47d9beca3a77bb509ad7b3ad84247efbc6d0619b","tid":2161246,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"129889a5050a014b55016140dc5ad12f8b64fa5b","tid":2161246,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21BUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=1d3f39c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"推左咁多日先得3萬幾人簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81434f6727a6bc00f54780a8910e202809